data.description: This stately four sided brick home sits a good distance off the road which provides you privacy on a 4 acre lot! There are 5 BR and 4 full bathrooms! There is one bedroom and one full bath located on the main level. The family room has wood floors and opens up to the dining room which connects to a relaxing sunroom. The kitchen has a breakfast room with french doors that open up to the back deck and fenced yard. There is a huge owner's suite with a sitting area and updated bathroom, including dual vanities, and a luxury shower system with jetted tub as well as a steam shower. The bonus room on the upper level could be a game room or 2nd den. There are a total of 3BR’s on the upper level. This home sits on a fully finished basement with a 5th bedroom and a full bathroom. There are utilities for a 2nd laundry room, and kitchen if you need to set the basement back up as an in-law suite. There is also a second driveway and private entrance. You have a parking pad for an RV/Boat, and there are pool hookups to the well & electrical for pool equipment already installed. Come and see all this home has to offer!
